rd.dev.simulation.model

Class DumpManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • rd.dev.simulation.datamanagement.DumpProvider

  • public class DumpManager
extends java.lang.Object
    handles requests for datadumps, diagnostics,etc

    separated from DataManager for better abstraction of DataManager methods - some of the dump methods are implementation-specific,such as csvWrite

    Author:
    afree

      • dumpUseValuesToCSV

        public void dumpUseValuesToCSV()
        Dump the usevalues to a csv file.

        Uses H2 SimpleResultSet and Csv classes which we populate from a JPA query by copying

        somewhat cumbersome but it seems that JPA doesn't allow us to get a plain old resultSet object directly from the database.

        And we don't want to go to the bother of creating a separate connection.

      • dumpStocksToCSV

        public void dumpStocksToCSV()

        Uses H2 SimpleResultSet and Csv classes which we populate from a JPA query by copying
